<HEADLINE>
<P>
TROOPS IN JAPAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A recent report related that the cost of maintaining 57,000 U.S. forces in 
Japan is $7 billion annually. As a taxpayer contributing to this enormous cost, 
I wonder who we are protecting Japan from. 
</P>
<P>
LEON SMITH 
</P>
<P>
Anaheim Hills 
</P>
