<TEXT>
<P>
TRW Seeks Order Barring Complaints: TRW Inc. sued Michael Jay &amp; Co., the 
self-proclaimed "credit-repair people," in Los Angeles Superior Court on 
Tuesday for allegedly advising people to dispute their credit records and swamp 
TRW with lawsuits. 
</P>
<P>
The suit said the actions Michael Jay &amp; Co. allegedly recommended were 
meant to hamper TRW's normal credit verification procedures. The suit seeks 
unspecified damages and a permanent injunction preventing the firm from telling 
people to file specious complaints. (Filed April 3, 1990. Case No. C757188) 
</P>
