</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
FANS; STREETS; PLACENTIA (CA) -- TRANSPORTATION; NAMES; BASEBALL PLAYERS; 
PLACENTIA (CA) -- ATHLETICS; BASEBALL HALL OF FAME 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
