 -- Telephone orders: Call Dodger ticket office at (213) 224-1400. Teletron at 
(213) 410-1062, (818) 763-9101 or (714) 634-1300. Tickets can be charged on 
Visa or Mastercard. Tickets ordered 10 days before a game will be mailed to 
customer. Tickets ordered after that time will be available on game day at the 
