Loge seating $8.00 
</P>
<P>
Upper reserved seating $8.00 
</P>
<P>
General admission* $4.00 
</P>
<P>
* General admission tickets are sold only on the day of the game, beginning at 
9 a.m. at Window C or at Gate B two hours before game time. 
</P>
<P>
Parking: $3 
</P>
